Add member types CRUD in admin settings + receipt payer_address everywhere

- Admin settings: full CRUD for member types (table, create/edit modal with live icon preview)
- Receipt modals: add payer_address input (admin + member create/edit)
- Auto-fill address when selecting member in receipt create form
- FeeController::buildPayerAddress changed to public static for reuse
- ActivityController::generateActivityReceipt now includes payer_address
- MemberController::confirmFeePayment uses MemberTypeModel + buildPayerAddress
- MemberController: removed hardcoded labels, uses getLabelMap()
- ReceiptController::searchMembers returns work_address, school_organization
